title: [Shattered Moors]
description: Tendrils of grey mist coil around the few low trees.  The mist is thick enough to obscure the lay of the terrain, but not so thick that it hides the pathway.  The topmost branches of the low trees are silhouetted by the cool bluish light of the moons.
